data.description: Single level home located minutes from the courthouse square and entertainment! There are 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms with a large bonus room and additional storage room. The kitchen has knotty pine cabinets and black appliances adding to it's rustic charm. 1 car garage with additional parking spaces in front. No HOA!  Appliances included. Cozy fenced backyard creates a serene and private setting. Just minutes from many hiking trails. Buyer to verify all facts about property including Square footage. All appliances convey in as is condition.
